extra : convert_revision : 7cc4e36e60bdd4834ba1784baf1d2e5037e5b1b5

A bunch of little fixes that were necessary to get staging running.

Add Force option to apply_and_push, push in hg.util
Fix matching of patch ids in autoland_queue(str => int)
Add bugid argument to bz.notify_bug() calls
Fix looping on bz_search_handler, which previously had a misplaced 'break'
This currently has lightweight try syntax for quick runs.
Fix work_dir navigation
Pass 'try' to has_sufficient permissions so that proper permissions will be checked on a try run.
Try to fix mq messages, it's on its way.
Fix fetching of next job from queue. Still *may* have an issue, need to test.
Change storage of patch lists in PatchSet object.
Add output to ldap_utils when getting permissions.
